{"source":"user-event","type":"click","text":"A\n    \n      New Standalone Page — /past-recipes\n      Create a brand new PastRecipesPage component at a new route. After finishing cooking, navigate to /past-recipes with a \"justFinished\" flag + the recipe name in route state. The page shows a congrats banner at the top when coming from cooking, then lists all past recipes below. MainPage gets a \"View Past Recipes\" button that navigates to the same route (without congrats).\n      \n        \n          Pros\n          \n            Clean separation — one page, one purpose\n            Reusable from both CookingPage and MainPage\n            Simple routing — just add one route\n          \n        \n        \n          Cons\n          \n            Similar to existing RecipeLibraryPage (some overlap)","choice":"a","id":null,"timestamp":1773817490770}
